# Input

```yml
  # Leading comment line spaces are
   # neither content nor indentation.
    
Not indented:
 By one space: |
    By four
      spaces
 Flow style: [    # Leading spaces
   By two,        # in flow style
  Also by two,    # are neither
  	Still by two   # content nor
    ]             # indentation.

```


# Prettier differences

```diff
--- Prettier
+++ Biome
@@ -2,12 +2,11 @@
 # neither content nor indentation.
 
 Not indented:
-  By one space: |
+ By one space: |
     By four
       spaces
-  Flow style: # Leading spaces
-    [
-      By two, # in flow style
-      Also by two, # are neither
-      Still by two, # content nor
-    ] # indentation.
+ Flow style: [    # Leading spaces
+   By two,        # in flow style
+  Also by two,    # are neither
+  	Still by two   # content nor
+    ]
```

# Output

```yml
# Leading comment line spaces are
# neither content nor indentation.

Not indented:
 By one space: |
    By four
      spaces
 Flow style: [    # Leading spaces
   By two,        # in flow style
  Also by two,    # are neither
  	Still by two   # content nor
    ]
```
